            <title><![CDATA[🛌#广东人午睡时间是全国第一# 搬砖人午睡，哪种睡姿比较好？[哈欠]最舒服的睡姿当然是在床上躺着睡呀[doge]！如果条件不允许，可以坐在椅子上，戴个U型枕仰躺...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[🛌<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%88%E7%9D%A1%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%88%E7%9D%A1%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#广东人午睡时间是全国第一#</span></a> 搬砖人午睡，哪种睡姿比较好？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哈欠]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_dahaqi-b1824d3d83.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>最舒服的睡姿当然是在床上躺着睡呀<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>！如果条件不允许，可以坐在椅子上，戴个U型枕仰躺着睡会儿。不建议以手臂代替枕头在桌上趴着睡，这样会压迫神经，使双臂、双手发麻，还可能导致颈部肌肉疲劳，引发颈椎问题。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（疾控科普）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hk9jic179qg206e061e81.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
