            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#儿科医生说口服药能解决的不建议输液#】肺炎支原体的临床表现是发热和剧烈、刺激干咳，绝大多数患者以轻症为主。⚠️医生提醒，正常情况下，口服药能解...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%B4%E5%8F%A3%E6%9C%8D%E8%8D%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E8%BE%93%E6%B6%B2%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E8%AF%B4%E5%8F%A3%E6%9C%8D%E8%8D%AF%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E8%BE%93%E6%B6%B2%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#儿科医生说口服药能解决的不建议输液#</span></a>】肺炎支原体的临床表现是发热和剧烈、刺激干咳，绝大多数患者以轻症为主。⚠️医生提醒，正常情况下，口服药能解决问题的，不建议去输液。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%86%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#感染肺炎支原体不一定是得了肺炎#</span></a>，也有可能是上呼吸道感染。 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4972235157340202" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hk86frnb10j61oc0xy7wh02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/swhGPIxLlx08asYbmR2E010412017yaF0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701076622&amp;ssig=kstac4w8mz&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ayD8NvY9lx08asY9XHa001041200B4vm0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701076622&amp;ssig=IYOm5FyyJC&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XRnNlVKllx08asY9GPio01041200nQ4z0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1701076622&amp;ssig=U2Wuxx3G%2BN&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4972235157340202" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
